Class AdvFilterController

  • java.lang.Object
    • seng202.group6.controller.AdvFilterController

  • public class AdvFilterController
extends java.lang.Object
    Controller class for the advanced filter which creates, deletes, views, and applies advanced filters to the data containers lists.

        static java.lang.Double[] parseRangeDouble(java.lang.String string)
        Accepts a string and converts it to a Double[2], representing a double range. If a number is missing it signifies +/- infinity as appropriate - this is represented in the output array as a null value.

        Returns:
        A Double array representation of the range.
